title: The water blocking tapes market is estimated to be USD 378 million in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 495 million by 2027, at a CAGR of 5.5% between 2022 and 2027
The market size of tab leads and tab seal film is projected to grow from USD 318 million in 2022 to USD 600 million by 2027, at a CAGR of 13.6%
